<p class="other-text">In early 2026 I participated in the 100 artist knockout competition "Unreal Björnament" by Björn Hurri. It's a 1v1 battle with one prompt and two weeks to submit an artwork, either illustration or concept art. The prompt for the first round was "The magical item granted otherworldly powers". The competition runs for multiple rounds, whereas only one winner per pair will participate in the next round.</p>


