<p class="other-text">In 2026 I designed a Twitch overlay for the Streamer <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/always__noob" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Always__Noob</a>. I created an overlay for a starting as well as just chatting screen and some info panels. Most of it was made with Krita, the animations were made with Adobe After Effects. There will be another overlay for a different type of content for this streamer in the future.</p>


